{"tid":675124,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"京阿尼歷代眼鏡娘Top 3","createTime":"2018-05-23T09:27:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T06:50:53.000Z","uid":183666,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9a46efcae1c93dd3369d25ef4b9d30098c3f3229","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"No. 3　田中明日香 （たなか あすか）<br />\n三年級生，使用的樂器是粗管上低音號。副樂團長，負責帶領樂團低音分部的職務。統率能力十分高，但並不想成為樂團長或副樂團長。曾說連當上副樂團長都是被百般請求才願意擔任副樂團長一職。一直在樂團的衝突中保持中立，從不講自己的想法。紅框眼鏡為其標誌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tv.anime-eupho.com/sp/img/character/asuka.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.anime-eupho.com%2Fsp%2Fimg%2Fcharacter%2Fasuka.png&h=bdd5ec76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/172506_c74b5e9cf1ff0b10bfc063155cdbbff3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F172506_c74b5e9cf1ff0b10bfc063155cdbbff3.jpg&h=05e5d3e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"26ae907db8606ffd03ed2a6ba23c9256c517c9b4","tid":675124,"uid":45373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:33:52.000Z","msg":"牙清u 又黎啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec62da0109e7462b613cf2ec3ea532c52bef016","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:43:04.000Z","msg":"No. 2　真鍋和（まなべ のどか）<br />\n和小唯自小就認識的玩伴，推薦小唯參加社團活動的人。有著深紅棕色的短髮，配戴著紅色的無頂框眼鏡。頭腦清晰，是學生會幹部，3年級時就任學生會長。因著唯的關係和輕音部成員成為好友。另外，也是澪後援會的主辦人（在曾我部學姐畢業後接任）。<br />\n姓氏取自The Pillows的真鍋吉明。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/173819_20a8fbfa3eeae49ac9ff58797f386dff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F173819_20a8fbfa3eeae49ac9ff58797f386dff.jpg&h=eaf34aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/51Xc68crGZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F51Xc68crGZL.jpg&h=853ae9df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f22f01315ce4d4d31a2f9da41726dd68bc962adb","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26ae907db8606ffd03ed2a6ba23c9256c517c9b4","tid":675124,"uid":45373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:33:52.000Z","msg":"牙清u 又黎啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T09:52:38.000Z","msg":"今次冇爭議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ab8eaa395c48d53d19bd69ebbf386dc8451654","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"5負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3c3e609fd58c5d69f8dba01cd05eb696d27522","tid":675124,"uid":34609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04ab8eaa395c48d53d19bd69ebbf386dc8451654","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"5負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"第一位呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb2a52f434bd2871a57f342025afc1af011c012","tid":675124,"uid":53126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c3c3e609fd58c5d69f8dba01cd05eb696d27522","tid":675124,"uid":34609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04ab8eaa395c48d53d19bd69ebbf386dc8451654","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"5負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"第一位呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"不愉快です？"},{"pid":"c907a7d588fc9b60e2187025287241a8a4bc0c15","tid":675124,"uid":34609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5fb2a52f434bd2871a57f342025afc1af011c012","tid":675124,"uid":53126,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c3c3e609fd58c5d69f8dba01cd05eb696d27522","tid":675124,"uid":34609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04ab8eaa395c48d53d19bd69ebbf386dc8451654","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:08:30.000Z","msg":"5負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"第一位呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"不愉快です？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"九成係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n京阿尼都無咩眼鏡娘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06869e4b0b796c324d077e24a3955ff6f2d98566","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"No. 1　栗山未來（くりやま みらい）<br />\n被秋人稱作「很適合戴眼鏡」的長月市立高中一年級生，劇場版未來篇起為二年級生，並成為了文藝部的副部長，是個擁有「被詛咒的血脈」、可操縱血液能力的異界士；右手上有無法回復的傷口，用異能操縱的血液從傷口流出，故平時得經常性纏著繃帶以止血。<br />\n平日相處較輕鬆，但會冷靜沉著地運用血液應戰。口頭禪為「我很不高興（不愉快です）」。<br />\n曾因殺死兒時玩伴伊波唯而感到自責，後因秋人的介入而解開心結。<br />\n興趣是園藝及更新部落格。因為把錢都拿去做園藝，所以經常缺錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/195911_522d8163262901c2da0a7ab5ab77a96f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F195911_522d8163262901c2da0a7ab5ab77a96f.jpg&h=61ada26c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/713v98mxhfL._SL1078_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F713v98mxhfL._SL1078_.jpg&h=3e5df7de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04e46407b96