37890,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:18:31.000Z","msg":"長門都無,樓主一定係00後小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e88451a43095343a17d6919bb75a4044174c13c","tid":675124,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"樓主真on9"},{"pid":"210a9b9bc7786d7c7942962dd9c7dab031e7b83b","tid":675124,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:25:52.000Z","msg":"樓主不如轉行做假膠"},{"pid":"22252ce884ca769958ca7ccbf8d973d1a8ee256c","tid":675124,"uid":19556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06869e4b0b796c324d077e24a3955ff6f2d98566","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:05:00.000Z","msg":"No. 1　栗山未來（くりやま みらい）<br />\n被秋人稱作「很適合戴眼鏡」的長月市立高中一年級生，劇場版未來篇起為二年級生，並成為了文藝部的副部長，是個擁有「被詛咒的血脈」、可操縱血液能力的異界士；右手上有無法回復的傷口，用異能操縱的血液從傷口流出，故平時得經常性纏著繃帶以止血。<br />\n平日相處較輕鬆，但會冷靜沉著地運用血液應戰。口頭禪為「我很不高興（不愉快です）」。<br />\n曾因殺死兒時玩伴伊波唯而感到自責，後因秋人的介入而解開心結。<br />\n興趣是園藝及更新部落格。因為把錢都拿去做園藝，所以經常缺錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/23/195911_522d8163262901c2da0a7ab5ab77a96f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F23%2F195911_522d8163262901c2da0a7ab5ab77a96f.jpg&h=61ada26c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/713v98mxhfL._SL1078_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F713v98mxhfL._SL1078_.jpg&h=3e5df7de&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:12:49.000Z","msg":"第1次認同樓豬"},{"pid":"7e66c499cd1f890a7ccc747af2548214b7f379ae","tid":675124,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22252ce884ca769958ca7ccbf8d973d1a8ee256c","tid":675124,"uid":19556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06869e4b0b796c324d077e24a3955ff6f2d98566","tid":675124,"u